259B-%25E5%2580%258B%25E6%25A1%2588%25E5%2590%2588%25E9%259B%2586-%25E9%2581%25AD%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%259C%258D%25E6%25AF%2586%25E5%258F%258D%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258E%25A7%25E8%25A5%25B2%25E8%25AD%25A6-%25E5%25AE%2598%25E6%258C%2587%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E9%259D%259E%25E8%25AA%25A0%25E5%25AF%25A6%25E8%25AD%2589%25E4%25BA%25BA-%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%2589%25BF%25E8%25AA%258D%25E8%25AD%2589%25E4%25BE%259B%25E8%25AA%2587%25E5%25A4%25A7%2F&d=4wcocBccBPvk8MIeFEbr%2BegMmE0tIaoAQI%2BAeX1JER4%3D&h=f5efeed2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E4%25BA%2582%25E4%25BD%259C%25E4%25BE%259B-%25E5%2580%258B%25E6%25A1%2588%25E5%2590%2588%25E9%259B%2586-%25E9%2581%25AD%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%259C%258D%25E6%25AF%2586%25E5%258F%258D%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258E%25A7%25E8%25A5%25B2%25E8%25AD%25A6-%25E5%25AE%2598%25E6%258C%2587%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E9%259D%259E%25E8%25AA%25A0%25E5%25AF%25A6%25E8%25AD%2589%25E4%25BA%25BA-%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%2589%25BF%25E8%25AA%258D%25E8%25AD%2589%25E4%25BE%259B%25E8%25AA%2587%25E5%25A4%25A7%2F&h=583d4de9\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E8%AD%A6%E4%BA%82%E4%BD%9C%E4%BE%9B-%E5%80%8B%E6%A1%88%E5%90%88%E9%9B%86-%E9%81%AD%E8%AD%A6%E5%9C%8D%E6%AF%86%E5%8F%8D%E8%A2%AB%E6%8E%A7%E8%A5%B2%E8%AD%A6-%E5%AE%98%E6%8C%87%E8%AD%A6%E9%9D%9E%E8%AA%A0%E5%AF%A6%E8%AD%89%E4%BA%BA-%E8%AD%A6%E6%89%BF%E8%AA%8D%E8%AD%89%E4%BE%9B%E8%AA%87%E5%A4%A7/</a>"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T13:50:53.000Z","msg":"睇完<br />\n痴撚線好多都屈得就屈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁班仆街警犬老屈完人有冇法律責任？<br />\n可唔可以告鳩番佢地轉頭？<br />\n可唔可以索取賠償（被告人）？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T14:28:57.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">講明先 小弟唔係咩專業人士</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實要睇情況<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n刑事嚟講可以用cap200 第33/39條告<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">但係唔易告得入</span> 因為要證明警察的口供有矛盾係<span style=\"color: red;\">故意</span>有一定難度( e.g.可以係因為 情況太混亂記錯 / 視覺上因為角度問題令警察誤會(佢自己唔覺得/唔知道自己講的唔係事實) <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">唔係幫黑警 而係刑事案入罪係要prove到3樣嘢<br />\n1.真係有犯罪的事實(畀了假口供) <br />\n2.有犯罪的意圖(e.g.警察講到明話佢要砌你生豬肉) (sorry我諗唔到有其他更好的例子證明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n3.無合理疑點 <br />\n所以法官話證人口供唔可信唔一定代表係證人特登落假口供</span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T15:22:25.000Z","msg":"屌咁班黑警咪鳩up無成本？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc425d5e3e0e2230e5e1c04f189a1ccfc6c10c19","tid":1324002,"uid":202876,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"132e9f1f945941ea6f28605f9da4921a9ce10a2c","tid":1324002,"uid":54303,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"quote":{"pid":"b48b1ddd2ef03b7c22f97ac1cd953f0efe8465d7","tid":1324002,"uid":185712,"like":3,"dislike":51,"score":-48,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T12:26:39.000Z","msg":"法庭就係咁"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T12:51:41.000Z","msg":"咁差佬屈哂機啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T15:25:39.000Z","msg":"係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以前冇cam冇片證明好慘<br />\n<br />\n宜家有can有片啲警察就呻做野煩左好多"},{"pid":"77257a3334ca55801bf5bb52242531ec25068737","tid":1324002,"uid":42164,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T15:31:49.000Z","msg":"by default係當證人講嘢準確、冇特別動機要講大話<br />\n辯方可以嘗試呈證據去攻擊證人整體可信性(general credibility)，或者話個證人喺呢單case裡面講大話<br />\n前者未必准呈堂，後者多數得<br />\n<br />\n以general credibility嚟講，係睇嗰個證人之前刑事紀錄或者disciplinary record<br />\n例如如果佢犯過同不誠實有關既罪行（盜竊等等），就可以話佢唔可信<br />\n最後都係法官/陪審團去判斷佢可唔可信<br />\n<br />\n所以係冇可能單純以警隊負面新聞/紀錄嚟話某個警員證人唔可信<br />\n都係要睇嗰個證人個人<br />\n控方有責任要披露控方證人有冇呢啲incredible既紀錄<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}